# Bazel is the BUILD GRAPH for this repo (affected-computation refinement via
# `runko-ci affected --engine bazel`, §14.5.4) - `bazel build //...` must stay
# green, but `go test` via `make check` remains the test truth. See
# docs/migration-findings.md for the migration record.
test --test_output=errors

# Release binaries (the Dockerfile's prebuilt mode): pure = CGO off, so
# every binary is static and runs on the alpine/musl runtime layer -
# the bazel equivalent of the source mode's CGO_ENABLED=0.
build:release --@rules_go//go/config:pure
